elements.name: Verify The Functionality of the R&L User Approve for Organization user

steps.name: The user has to Navigate to the IHC login page
The user has to login with a valid user crential for R&L user
The user has to click the  Registration/Renewal dropdown and click the Request List
The user has to click the action of the eye icon for the required user to be approved
The user has to select Approved from the dropdownMenu
The user has to give feedback and update the status of the request for the Organization
The user has to verify Whether the Successfully approved Organization Application
